THRILLING RESULTS OF ARRC ROUND 2 MALAYSIA! 

What a wild ride at the Malaysian circuit! The race got off to a dramatic start, with multiple crashes bringing out the caution flag. But when the green flag waved again, the real battle began! 

Hiroki Ono fought hard to take the lead, pushing Ramdan Rosli to his limits. Meanwhile, Sarthak Chavan and Luis Miguel were locked in a fierce battle for third and fourth.

But in a stunning turn of events, Hiroki’s engine braking in the final turn sent him tumbling down to fourth place! 

This opened the door for @lopezrodriguezluismiguel to snatch the win, with @ramdanrosli taking second and @sarthakchavan075 claiming third! 

What an electrifying finish! The championship standings are heating up!

#TVSMotorCompany #TVSRacing #TVSApacheSeries #TVSAsiaOMC2025 #ARRC #Round2

latestPosts.caption:
“THRILLING RACE 1 RESULTS AT ARRC ROUND 2! 🔥

Ramdan Rosli dominates the track, taking the top spot on the podium! 🏆 A thrilling win on home turf! 🇲🇾

Hiroki Ono puts up a strong fight, finishing in 2nd place. Despite a strong performance, he narrowly misses the top spot.

Sarthak Chavan shows remarkable determination, securing 3rd place! 💪 He’s continued to push hard, maintaining his position in the championship standings.

What an electrifying race with dramatic position changes! The championship is heating up! 🔥 Who’s your favorite to take the win in the next race? 🤔
